For 100 points, ensure one of your 30-value liquids is magical (either extracted or filtered) and the other is mundane. Combining two magical or two mundane 30-value liquids will yield 60 points. Avoid using Vial on liquids/gases, or Filter on already extracted items, as these actions result in negative or lower values.

message: Focus on using 'filter' on gas (magical/mundane) or liquid magical items; they consistently yield +30 value. Use 'vial' on solid mundane items for a +30 extract.
